title: How to Earn a Cashback Bonus with AssetsFx Trading
content:
https://www.fxvnpro.com/how-to-earn-a-cashback-bonus-with-assetsfx-trading/
 Table of Contents

 	Introduction
 	Understanding the AssetsFx Cashback Bonus Program

 	1. Instant Cash Back
 	2. AssetsFx Rebate Program


 	Additional Information to Consider
 	Conclusion

Introduction
If you’re a trader looking to boost your earnings, the AssetsFx Cashback Bonus program is designed just for you. This program rewards you for your trading activities, allowing you to earn cashback on the trades you make. Here’s a comprehensive guide on how to earn cashback with AssetsFx and make the most of their promotional offers.
Understanding the AssetsFx Cashback Bonus Program
AssetsFx offers two primary promotional opportunities under its cashback bonus program: the Instant Cash Back and the Rebate Program. Each has its unique structure and benefits tailored to different trading volumes and preferences.
1. Instant Cash Back
Eligibility:
To qualify for the Instant Cash Back offer, you need to open a live trading account and make a minimum deposit of $500 or its equivalent in supported cryptocurrencies. This offer is available to both new and existing clients.

Cashback Rate:
Once you’ve met the deposit requirement, you can earn $1 cashback for every lot traded on forex pairs and metals. This can add up quickly, especially if you’re an active trader.

How to Request:
After activating your trading account and meeting the deposit requirement, you need to individually request to join the cashback program. This is a crucial step to ensure you start earning cashback.

Restrictions:
It’s important to note that this cashback bonus offer cannot be combined with other promotions. Additionally, if your account is already linked to an Introducing Broker (IB), you won’t be eligible for this offer.

Withdrawability:
One of the standout features of this program is that the cashback you earn is fully withdrawable. This means you can transfer your earnings directly to your bank account or use them for additional trading.
2. AssetsFx Rebate Program
Structure:
The AssetsFx rebate program offers a tiered cashback system that rewards you based on the volume of your trades:

 	10% cashback for trading between 10 to 100 lots.
 	20% cashback for trading between 100 to 500 lots.
 	25% cashback for trading over 1000 lots.

This tiered structure is designed to incentivize higher trading volumes, providing more substantial rewards for more active traders.

Eligibility:
The rebate program is available to all clients, whether you have a Standard or an ECN account. However, you must register for the rebate program separately to start earning cashback based on your trading volume.
Additional Information to Consider
Minimum Deposit:
While the minimum deposit for participating in the cashback bonus program is typically $500, AssetsFx may accept lower amounts for other account types. However, to maximize your cashback earnings, a $500 deposit is recommended.

Trading Instruments:
AssetsFx offers a wide array of trading instruments, including forex pairs, cryptocurrencies, indices, and commodities. This variety allows you to diversify your forex cashback trading strategies and increase your potential for earning cashback.

Regulatory Status:
AssetsFx is registered in St. Vincent and the Grenadines. While this provides a level of flexibility, it’s essential to consider the regulatory oversight when deciding to trade with this broker. Make sure you’re comfortable with this aspect before proceeding.
Conclusion
The AssetsFx Cashback Bonus and rebate programs provide a fantastic opportunity for traders to earn additional income from their trading activities. Whether you’re a new or experienced trader, these trading promotions offer valuable incentives that can significantly enhance your trading profitability. By understanding the eligibility requirements, cashback rates, and how to participate, you can make the most of these offers and earn cashback trading forex with AssetsFx.
